Exim4 setup for SMTorP, SMTP over Tor
=====================================

Based on the recipies found on.
https://johannes.sipsolutions.net/Projects/exim-tor-hidden-mail/faq/
https://johannes.sipsolutions.net/Projects/exim-tor-hidden-mail/

There are also recipes for postfix 
http://www.void.gr/kargig/blog/2014/05/10/smtp-over-hidden-services-with-postfix/
and transport via ssh, http://log.or.cz/?p=332 .

Contact Petter Reinholdtsen <pere@hungry.com> if you have comments or improvements.
The code is available from
https://github.com/petterreinholdtsen/exim4-smtorp
